sentences: Rodney Ramone Hill Jr. (born December 28, 1979), better known by his stage name Rocko, is an American rapper, songwriter, and record executive.
Rocko released his first and only major studio album, Self Made, in 2008 through a joint venture with Island Records and Jermaine Dupri's
In 2010, Hill founded the A1 Recordings record label and signed fellow Atlanta artist Future, who would come to achieve worldwide success.
